{"tid":1135561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大灣區】廣東開放53國免簽過境144小時 港或間接受益","createTime":"2019-05-02T11:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T12:40:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"586dd349fe1d6629cdc56ed124661acff3d453b1","tid":1135561,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"【大灣區】廣東開放53國免簽過境144小時 港或間接受益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2340458/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE53%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%8D%E7%B0%BD%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83144%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%20%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%96%E9%96%93%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2340458%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE53%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25A2%2583144%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%2520%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%259B%258A&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=4a2ec95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2340458/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE53%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%8D%E7%B0%BD%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83144%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%20%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%96%E9%96%93%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東省今天起給予53個國家公民免簽證過境144小時，以推動粵港澳大灣區發展。此前廣東只給予外國人72小時免簽證入境，而且入境口岸限定白雲機場。<br />\n<br />\n《南方都市報》今天報道，經國務院批准，廣東當局自今日起實施外國人144小時過境免簽政策，目的是方便外國人在廣東的出入境，吸引更多外國人赴粵觀光旅遊和參與經濟社會建設，為粵港澳大灣區經濟發展發揮積極作用。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，過境外國人可選擇從廣州白雲機場、深圳寶安機場、揭陽潮汕機場空港口岸中的任何一個口岸入境，並從廣東具備客運功能的32個對外開放口岸中的任何一個口岸出境；其中包括可通往香港的機場、公路、鐵路、港口的多個口岸，此舉能為香港帶來過境人流，令香港間接受益。<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，廣東只給予外國人72小時從廣州白雲機場過境免簽政策，新措施增加了入出境口岸和停留時間。<br />\n<br />\n或為港帶來過境人流<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，為了確保新措施順利實施，廣東各入境口岸還會設立過境免簽專用通道，簡化查驗流程。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述相關單位負責人說，新措施將會把廣東打造成為重要的國際旅遊目的地，提升廣東開放型經濟水準並建設成為中國的重要國際門戶。"},{"pid":"f73bbd05b1ded77957a6edf61e2819d86c246605","tid":1135561,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"邊53？"},{"pid":"c613a5c8348b7cbe90d2d11103fe8eab83dfdf0d","tid":1135561,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"成日覺得廣東機場有d雞肋"},{"pid":"5f44d36063d995dea5ba30fb647fc41be5292285","tid":1135561,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c613a5c8348b7cbe90d2d11103fe8eab83dfdf0d","tid":1135561,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"成日覺得廣東機場有d雞肋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"*州"},{"pid":"bcddbdc6cee9f2d2d1cb19ec529d81f07593774c","tid":1135561,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"成6日過咩境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e74c95fd84069d88906c69771cdbd89810d897","tid":1135561,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"三元里 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經割讓左比非洲<br />\n果53個國家九成係非洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11edbfc60d17ea0122bc0f5848cabb385e51616","tid":1135561,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcddbdc6cee9f2d2d1cb19ec529d81f07593774c","tid":1135561,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"成6日過咩境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"係咪要有機票果隻過境??"},{"pid":"7bf3fa44c4df437b491407144f6ae0ca2065e5f8","tid":1135561,"uid":41428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"標題寫完「或」，再加埋「間接」，真係點吹都得<br />\n<br />\n中國或間接成最大贏家"},{"pid":"5ed1c915669d3118ce7c99472